  "body": "Executing `await time.increase(123)` throws \r\n\r\n> TypeError: web3.currentProvider.sendAsync is not a function\r\n\r\n**üíª Environment**\r\n\r\nUsing openzeppelin-solidity@2.0.0 and trying to execute the statement above inside a `truffle test` run. OS is Ubuntu 18.04.1 with Truffle@5.0.0\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nConsole-logging `web3.currentProvider` returns `undefined`.\r\n\r\n**üî¢ Code to reproduce bug**\r\n\r\nJust a Truffle JS test file including following lines.\r\n```\r\nconst time = require(\"openzeppelin-solidity/test/helpers/time\");\r\nawait time.increase(123);\r\n```\r\n",
